                    "content": "<p><span class=\"font-size-small\">Smartboard-site (NL)  <a href=\"http://www.smartopschool.nl/\" target=\"_self\">Smart op school</a></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-small\">Smartboard-site (EN)  <a href=\"http://www.smarttech.com/\" target=\"_self\">Smarttech</a></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-small\">Smart trainingsmateriaal (NL): <a href=\"http://www.smartboard.nl/nl/training.php\" target=\"_self\">http://www.smartboard.nl/nl/training.php</a></span></p>\n<p> <span class=\"font-size-small\">De rode planeet</span> <a href=\"http://www.drp.nl/digibord//Producten.html\" target=\"_self\"><span class=\"font-size-small\">http://www.drp.nl/digibord//Producten.html</span></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n"
